== a long flag matches its whole name, not a prefix:
shit: 1:33: error: Unknown flag '--helpXYZ'.
== false ignores --help and returns 1:
rc=1
== exit masks an out-of-range status to 8 bits in a subshell:
44
== unset of an array element is not glob-expanded under failglob:
x z
== a re-read arithmetic variable is not folded stale after a side effect:
5 6 6
